title: Embracing Imposter Syndrome
description: Have you ever looked around a room and thought, everyone here knows more than me? Entered a race knowing that you'll be one of the last to finish? What about looking at a developer conference schedule that you are speaking at and had to Google half the words? Sometimes it’s not imposter syndrome, sometimes you are an imposter but why should that hold you back? Let’s accept it and see what we can achieve.
